#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be sure to compare the second example of a hit with the first example of a "
"reflection."
msgstr "Võrdle kindlasti tabamuse teist näidet peegelduse esimese näitega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Liidese tutvustus"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Board Description"
msgstr "Mängulaua kirjeldus"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kblackbox; Game Board</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kblackbox;i mängulaud</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kblackbox; Game Board</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kblackbox;i mängulaud</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following types of field are found on the game board:"
msgstr "Mängulaual võib näha järgmisi elemente:"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The big black box in the middle"
msgstr "Suur must kast keskel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you must mark the positions you think a ball is in."
msgstr "Siin tuleb ära märkida ruudud, kus arvad palli olevat."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lasers around the box"
msgstr "Laserid kasti ümber"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lasers are shooting beams of light when switched on. Then, they "
"disappear and are replaced by an information about the interactions of the "
"laser beam with the balls in the black box."
msgstr ""
"Laserid tulistavad kiire välja ja seejärel kaovad, jättes endast maha teabe "
"selle kohta, mis juhtus kiirega kastis."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balls"
msgstr "Pallid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>There must be one there!</quote> you think. These mark where you "
"suspect a ball is placed in the black box."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Siin peab küll üks olema!</quote> arvad sa. Need märgivad kohta, kus "
"sa arvad mustas ruudus peituvat palli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "At the end of the game, the right and wrong positions of the balls are "
#| "also marked with \"balls\"."
msgid ""
"At the end of the game, the right and wrong positions of the balls are also "
"marked with <quote>balls</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Mängu lõpus tähistatakse ka pallide õiged ja valed asukohad \"pallidega\"."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Markers for \"free position\""
msgstr "\"Vaba asukoha\" markerid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use them to mark some positions where you are sure there is no ball."
msgstr ""
"Nendega saab märkida asukohad, kus sinu arvates kindlasti palli ei asu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
