#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Mäng</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Näita rekordeid</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the high score tables."
msgstr "Näitab rekordite tabelit."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start Tutorial</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mäng</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Treening</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start the tutorial of the game. This is a user friendly way to learn the "
"game rules."
msgstr ""
"Käivitab mängu tutvustuse. See on kasutajasõbralik viis saada selgeks "
"mängureeglid."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Sandbox Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mäng</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uus liivakastimäng</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode, the solution is displayed at the start of the game. This is "
"useful to understand the game principles."
msgstr ""
"Selles režiimis näidatakse juba alguses lahendust. Sellest on abi mängu "
"põhimõtete omandamisel."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Mäng</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Välju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "This closes the window and quits &kblackbox;."
msgstr "Sulgeb akna ja lõpetab &kblackbox;i töö."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Solve</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lahenda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use it to give up a game. It shows you the solution: the right positions of "
"the balls."
msgstr ""
"Selle abil saab mängu kiiresti lõpetada: valimisel näidatakse lahendust ehk "
"pallide tegelikku asukohta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Done!</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Valmis!</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you placed all the balls, choose \"Done!\" to terminate the current "
#| "game, to compute the final score and to display the real positions of the "
#| "balls."
msgid ""
"When you placed all the balls, choose <guilabel>Done!</guilabel> to "
"terminate the current game, to compute the final score and to display the "
"real positions of the balls."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled kõik pallid asetanud, siis lõpetab see käsk mängu, arvutab "
"lõpptulemuse ning näitab ära pallide tegeliku asukoha."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guisubmenu>Raskusaste</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the game difficulty. Harder games have more balls and bigger black "
"box than easier games. You can also play with a custom difficulty level that "
"you can set up in the setting dialog of &kblackbox;."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab määrata mängu raskusastme. Raskemas mängus on rohkem palle ja "
"suurem must kast kui lihtsamas. Samuti võib mängida kohandatud "
"raskusastmega, mille tingimused saab kindlaks määrata &kblackbox;i "
"seadistustedialoogis."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note: games with 4 balls or less can always be solved with certainty! "
#| "That is not the case for games with 5 balls or more."
msgid ""
"Games with 4 balls or less can always be solved with certainty! That is not "
"the case for games with 5 balls or more."
msgstr ""
"Märkus: nelja või vähema palliga mänge saab kindlasti alati lahendada. Viie "
"või enama palli puhul võíb asi mõnigi kord päris keeruline olla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Additionally &kblackbox; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
