#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. You can use the directional keys to control the cursor, &Enter; to "
#| "place and remove balls, and <keycap>Spacebar</keycap> to place 'empty' "
#| "marks."
msgid ""
"Yes. You can use the directional keys to control the cursor, &Enter; to "
"place and remove balls, and &Space; to place <quote>empty</quote> marks."
msgstr ""
"Jah. Kursori liikumist saab juhtida nooleklahvidega, &Enter; võimaldab palle "
"asetada ja eemaldada ning <keycap>tühikuklahv</keycap> asetada tühja ruudu "
"markereid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Ma pean mängust väljuma, aga mäng ei ole veel läbi. Kas ma saan oma seisu "
"salvestada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kblackbox; has no save feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kblackbox; ei paku praegu salvestamisvõimalust."

